aris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than a stadium, the organizers are turning one of the world's most famous waterways, the River Seine, into the world's biggest theatrical stage.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A four-mile-long flotilla of nearly 100 boats will carry thousands of athletes from more than 200 countries past hundreds of thousands of spectators seated on the banks of The Seine and finish at the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3802405717876673e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are excited that Maria, who anchors the most watched studio show in sports on NFL Sundays, will host our Late Night show with one of the world's greatest cities as her stage,\\\" saidMolly Solomon, Executive Producer and President, NBC Olympics Production.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9150303414576658, \"rank\": 0.09285993532331639, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9998271454463796, \"rank\": 0.00017288429873937362, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\"}, {\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\", \"score\": 0.9994542733243641, \"rank\": 0.0005460180360979006, \"text\": \"Executive Producer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\"}, {\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each night under the Parisian lights, she will put her stamp on the day, with a look at the must-watch moments and best events, and some surprise guests stopping by.\\\"\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ever since I attended the Atlanta Olympics in 1996, it was a dream of mine to compete in the Games, which has now evolved to covering them,\\\" said Taylor.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As host of the Late Night show, I am excited to tell the best stories of the day while moving about the city and hosting from the venues, cafes, plazas, and famous landmarks of Paris, one of the world's most inspirational cities.\\\"\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.191838029545037e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This week, Taylor will be in Paris hosting NBC Sports' semifinals and finals coverage of Roland-Garros tennis matches from June 6-9.\", \"from\": 2